Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.00,0:23:12.61,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}夜に舞う
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.87,0:23:14.99,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}震えるながら
